1. *Bojiš* se da ćeš izgubiti svoju priliku. (You are scared to lose your chance.)

2. Ona je popila *bojiš* vode. (She drank colored water.)

3. On je *bojiš* oči. (He has colored eyes.)

4. Ona je *bojiš* nokte lakom. (She painted her nails with nail polish.)

5. Mi smo *bojiš* sliku. (We colored the picture.)

6. Oni su se *bojiš* u dvorištu. (They were playing in the yard.)

7. Ona je *bojiš* svoje lokne. (She colored her curls.)